'''羅賓·艾伦·西克'''（{{lang-en|'''Robin Alan Thicke'''({{IPAc-en|ˈ|θ|ɪ|k}})}}，{{bd|1977年|3月10日|}}）<ref>{{cite book |author=Thicke, Alan |title=How Men Have Babies: The Pregnant Father's Survival Guide |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Jo7KxZEOXQ8C |year=2003 |publisher=Jodere Group |isbn=978-1-58872-060-3 |access-date=2013-08-30 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231123709/http://books.google.com/books?id=Jo7KxZEOXQ8C |dead-url=no }}</ref> 是一位出生于[[美国|美国]]的[[加拿大|加拿大]][[唱作人|唱作人]]、[[唱片制作人|唱片制作人]]和[[演员|演员]]<ref>Concepcion, Mariel (July 2, 2008). [http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1044919/thicke-says-world-needs-something-else "Thicke Says World Needs 'Something Else'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1044919/thicke-says-world-needs-something-else |date=20201021193741 }}. ''[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]''.</ref>。他是演员[[艾倫·錫克|艾倫·錫克]]和演员[[Gloria_Loring|Gloria Loring]]的儿子。西克曾与许多明星一起工作，如[[克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉|克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉]]、[[妮琪·米娜|妮琪·米娜]]、[[珍妮佛·哈德遜|珍妮佛·哈德遜]]、[[亚瑟小子|亚瑟小子]]和[[玛丽·布莱姬|玛丽·布莱姬]]等，还参与了许多热门音乐专辑的制作。<ref name="Duets">{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20576801,00.html |title=Kelly Clarkson Among Singers Starring in Duets |publisher=''People Magazine'' |date=2012-03-08 |accessdate=2012-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120421023714/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20576801,00.html |archivedate=2012-04-21 }}</ref>

羅賓·西克和搭檔菲董（Pharrell Williams）共同演唱的《模糊界線》（''Blurred Lines''），获得了'''[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]連續12週冠军'''，成为西克的第一支冠军单曲。然而，這首歌後來卻被控抄襲已故靈魂歌手[[马文·盖伊|马文·盖伊]]（Marvin Gaye）1977年的作品《Got to Give It Up》。2015年3月10號判決出爐，美國洛城法院做出判決，兩人必須賠償[[马文·盖伊|马文·盖伊]]（Marvin Gaye）家屬740萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/6502012/could-pharrells-happy-be-the-next-target-of-a-copyright-lawsuit |title=美國告示牌官網2015-03-13新聞資料 |access-date=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2015-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316010413/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/6502012/could-pharrells-happy-be-the-next-target-of-a-copyright-lawsuit |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/robin-thicke-and-pharrell-lose-blurred-lines-lawsuit-20150310 |title=美國滾石雜誌官網2015-03-10新聞資料 |access-date=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2018-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180222113529/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/robin-thicke-and-pharrell-lose-blurred-lines-lawsuit-20150310 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.storm.mg/article/43601 |title=羅賓西克、菲董抄襲老前輩判賠2.3億元 |newspaper=[[風傳媒|風傳媒]] |date=2015-03-11 |access-date=2019-01-31 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2019-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730151340/https://www.storm.mg/article/43601 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/477418 |title=菲董、羅賓西克洗腦歌《模糊界線》抄襲判賠2.2億 |newspaper=[[ETtoday|ETtoday]]星光雲 |date=2015-03-12 |access-date=2019-01-31 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2019-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422173414/https://star.ettoday.net/news/477418 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

